What is Gold-Filled?Gold-filled is an economical alternative to solid gold. By law, it has 1/20th (or 5%) by weight layer of 14 karat gold permanently bonded over a core of base metal. It is tarnish-resistant, safe for sensitive skin and unlike gold plate, it will not wear off. It is a great way to enjoy affordable gold jewelry. Do not mistake Gold-Filled jewelry for plated jewelry as there is no comparison. Gold-filled jewelry is fine jewelry that is in fact fifteen times as thick as plated jewelry and can therefore be worn on a daily basis.
